\begin{definition}%对0开头的状态和1开头的状态进行定义
Let $S_0$ denote the set of states $\{(0,x_1,x_2,...,x_{n-1})|x_1,x_2,...,x_{n-1}\in \mathcal{D}\}$, and let $S_1$ denote the set of states $\{(1,x_1,x_2,...,x_{n-1})|x_1,x_2,...,x_{n-1}\in \mathcal{D}\}$.
